{"word":"μέλος","slug":"μέλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μέλος, ους, τό</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘part of a bodily structure’, <b>member,</b> as part of one’s body <b><a href='B:470 5:29'>Mt 5:29</a>; <a href='B:520 6:13'>Ro 6:13</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Ro; <b><a href='B:530 12:12'>1 Cor 12:12</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in the same <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ch.\">ch.</a>; <b><a href='B:660 3:5'>Js 3:5f</a>; <a href='B:660 4:1'>4:1</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> in imagery, of interpersonal connection, <b>member <a href='B:520 12:5'>Ro 12:5</a>; <a href='B:530 6:15'>1 Cor 6:15</a>; <a href='B:530 12:27'>12:27</a>; <a href='B:560 4:16'>Eph 4:16</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>, 25; <a href='B:560 5:30'>5:30</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μέλλω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Μελχί\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}